1/* $NetBSD: vtof.c,v 1.1.1.1 2012/03/23 21:20:10 christos Exp $ */

3#include "ipf.h"
4
5int
6vtof(version)
7 int version;
8{
9#ifdef USE_INET6
10 if (version == 6)
11 return AF_INET6;
12#endif
13 if (version == 4)
14 return AF_INET;
15 if (version == 0)
16 return AF_UNSPEC;
17 return -1;
18}
